                  </persName>
               
            . I am the <rs id="t18220417-188-viclabel991" type="occupation">wife</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-188-victim1739 t18220417-188-viclabel991"></join> of George Sanderson. On the 12th of March, about twelve o'clock. I was in Spitalfields Market, and lost a handkerchief from the bottom of a flag basket; it had a quantity of garden stuff over it. The officer seized the prisoner with it - it was safe just before.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182204170069"></xptr>
            
                  <persName id="t18220417-188-person1740">
