                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I was in the market and heard a cry - the prisoner ran by me; I took him, and found the handkerchief in his bosom.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I gave 6 d. for it.</p>
